                    "webTitle": "Cruel Intentions review – young love still looks laboured 21 years on",
                    "webUrl": "https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/jul/17/cruel-intentions-review-ryan-phillippe-sarah-michelle-gellar-reese-witherspoon",
