                    "webTitle": "Harriet review – Cynthia Erivo is sublime as legendary slave rebel",
                    "webUrl": "https://www.theguardian.com/film/2019/sep/11/harriet-review-toronto-film-festival",
                    "apiUrl": "https://content.guardianapis.com/film/2019/sep/11/harriet-review-toronto-film-festival",
